lead_paragraph: Miami Marlins manager Don Mattingly said it was an easy decision to pull Adam Conley after 116 pitches despite the lefty having not allowed a hit for 7 2/3 innings.

headline.print_headline: Conley Pulled in 8th With No-Hit Bid, Miami Hangs On
